![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/57e87c88-135f-40e5-b9ec-4fcec63f0ec2/20240524_191727.jpg?format=original)

Kevin Owens returns to help Randy Orton before he’s jumped by the Bloodline.